    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE BOOK OF BUJA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/5fb6b70486ba988d44a5c4db042d4e5a.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/5fb6b70486ba988d44a5c4db042d4e5a.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/5fb6b70486ba988d44a5c4db042d4e5a.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The<strong> Queen of Darrow</strong> is dead. The <strong>King</strong> is on trial for her death and has asked you,<strong> Buja</strong>, to help clear his name. Using your ability to peer into a <i>corpse's final moments</i>, you follow a trail of <strong>remains</strong> to uncover the context of her demise and, hopefully, save the <strong>King and the Kingdom</strong> from an <i>impending disaster</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Various Fruits and Shoot Them as Projectiles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/7aa7508e5f8e9e31afe2d2d86ba73d34.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/7aa7508e5f8e9e31afe2d2d86ba73d34.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/7aa7508e5f8e9e31afe2d2d86ba73d34.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stack</strong> various combinations of <strong>fruit</strong> on your <strong>spear</strong>. Each <strong>fruit</strong> does something different!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Translate Ancient Texts with a Seer Stone</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/6095e9e4499ad604179950140b172d54.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/6095e9e4499ad604179950140b172d54.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/6095e9e4499ad604179950140b172d54.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find Hidden Meaning in People's Words</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/e88dc37c7be9be7d14a6bb5dc4bd7155.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/e88dc37c7be9be7d14a6bb5dc4bd7155.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reveal subt<strong>let</strong>ies with the Mind Maggot, a gri<strong>me</strong>y, yet <strong>know</strong>ledgeable l<strong>if</strong>eform that burrows deep in <strong>you</strong>r ear <strong>can</strong>al and highlights th<strong>read</strong>s of <strong>me</strong>aning in text that you read.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover the Mysteries of the Dead</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/397da922ec303c667f16b5ba89f14ac1.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/397da922ec303c667f16b5ba89f14ac1.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/397da922ec303c667f16b5ba89f14ac1.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your inherited ability to <strong>peer into the dead</strong> and solve the mystery behind the <strong>Queen's death</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find All of Your Elephant Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/4350424563cc2ad364cad69db3b0ca95.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/4350424563cc2ad364cad69db3b0ca95.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/4350424563cc2ad364cad69db3b0ca95.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Electrify Water to Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/a86adbcfa64811879e567fe3465f055a.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/a86adbcfa64811879e567fe3465f055a.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/a86adbcfa64811879e567fe3465f055a.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Freeze Bushes to Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/16cad953a4809ffa63d66046beb17356.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/16cad953a4809ffa63d66046beb17356.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/16cad953a4809ffa63d66046beb17356.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Dozens of Interesting Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/16fd2633e1ec156ffb475720212ad316.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/16fd2633e1ec156ffb475720212ad316.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/16fd2633e1ec156ffb475720212ad316.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/4389b57428132ff2cdc213135b03e655.poster.avif?t=1728922109\" width=512 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/4389b57428132ff2cdc213135b03e655.webm?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1785580/extras/4389b57428132ff2cdc213135b03e655.mp4?t=1728922109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
